Rio_Rancho.V. Sue Cleveland High School: V. Sue Cleveland High School or better known as Cleveland High School, (CHS) is a public senior high school of the Rio Rancho Public Schools. It is located in north-western Rio Rancho, New Mexico. Named after long time Rio Rancho Superintendent and educator of Public Schools, V. Sue Cleveland was established in 2009, due to overcrowding at Rio Rancho High School.
